These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, tomato, zucchini, blueberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, metal, gospel, hip-hop
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, dutch, spanish, chinese
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, goat, snake
 1. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 2. the person eating corn is in an even position##4
 3. the turkish is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
 4. the spanish is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
 7. the dutch is the person eating zucchini##1
 8. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the snake and the fan of hip-hop##2
10. the person eating corn is the owner of the snake##1
11. the fan of gospel is the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | zucchini  | corn    | blueberry    | tomato   |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | soul   | gospel       | hip-hop    |
| Nationality   | dutch | turkish | chinese    | spanish |
| Pet           | dog | snake       | bird | goat     |

