.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, grapes, cabbage, cauliflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, camping, card-games, board-games
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, pakistani, dutch, polish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, water-polo, skiing, parkour
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
 2. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 4. the person eating grapes is the egyptian##1
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the egyptian is on the left or right of the dutch##3
 7. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 8. the polish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
 9. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
11. the dutch is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | lettuce  | grapes    | cabbage     | cauliflower       |
| Hobby         | card-games | board-games | singing   | camping |
| Nationality   | dutch | egyptian   | pakistani   | polish    |
| Sport         | skiing | parkour  | surfing | water-polo   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, 7up, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, software-developer, teacher, coach
There are 4 different nationalities: french, malaysian, brazilian, thai
4 different pets are kept: cat, snake, frog, horse
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the journalist##3
 2. the malaysian is the teacher##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 4. the journalist is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is the coach##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 7. the owner of the cat is the thai##1
 8. the coach is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the french##1
10. the owner of the cat is the person drinking 7up##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | 7up   | almond-milk    | lemonade      |
| Job           | teacher | journalist | software-developer | coach     |
| Nationality   | malaysian      | thai   | french   | brazilian |
| Pet           | horse         | cat       | frog  | snake       |

