.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, almond-milk, coffee
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, avocado, pomegranate, cauliflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, cooking, singing, camping
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, snowboarding, rugby, skiing
 1. the person drinking juice is the person eating strawberry##1
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 8. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
10. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating cauliflower##1
12. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee       | almond-milk   | juice   | cola   |
| Food       | avocado        | cauliflower | strawberry    | pomegranate       |
| Hobby      | camping | cooking    | singing  | dancing |
| Sport      | snowboarding  | rugby  | cricket | skiing    |

