.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, peach, onion, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, writing, chess, card-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, doctor, freelancer, police-officer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, sailing, badminton, tennis
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person eating zucchini##2
 3. the freelancer is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 4. the doctor is the person eating peas##1
 5. the engineer is on the left or right of the doctor##3
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating peach is the engineer##1
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is the doctor##1
 9. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
10. the doctor is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | onion    | zucchini      | peas          | peach    |
| Hobby   | writing | card-games       | chess | traveling |
| Job     | police-officer     | freelancer      | doctor     | engineer |
| Sport   | sailing   | tennis | badminton        | parkour   |

