.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, peas, tomato, plum
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, salsa, jazz, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, french, japanese, chinese
 1. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 3. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of ambient is between the japanese and the fan of salsa##2
 7. the fan of jazz is the person eating tomato##1
 8. the person drinking milk is the person eating tomato##1
 9. the french is on the far right##1
10. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate  | milk    | almond-milk       | soy-milk       |
| Food          | plum    | tomato | peas | pomegranate     |
| Music-Genre   | techno | jazz        | ambient    | salsa   |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | japanese      | chinese    | french |

