 6. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
 9. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
10. the spanish is on the far right##1
11. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
12. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
