 1. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the pony##2
 3. the japanese is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 4. the person watching musical movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the chinese is on the right of the thai##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 7. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the german##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the japanese and the person watching time-travel movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
11. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
12. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3

