The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, badminton, biathlon, handball
 1. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of funk is between the person watching adventure movies and the person who's sport is badminton##2
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 5. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 7. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is handball is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person eating cabbage is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
11. the person eating cabbage is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of classical is on the left of the person eating radish##1
13. the fan of metal is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
