 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 3. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
10. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
11. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade       | coffee | almond-milk        | iced-tea        |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | hiking       | drawing | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | crime     | romance        | comedy    | disaster      |
| Sport         | snowboarding     | parkour    | cricket | swimming   |

