.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, metal, salsa, blues
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, dutch, american, colombian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon, baseball, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, roller, train, jet-ski
 1. the fan of blues is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is between the nigerian and the colombian##2
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the dutch##1
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 6. the fan of metal is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 8. the colombian is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
10. the nigerian is in an even position##4
11. the nigerian is on the far right##1
12. the fan of r&b is on the right of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | r&b | blues     | salsa        |
| Nationality   | american | colombian  | dutch     | nigerian |
| Sport         | biathlon    | swimming | baseball      | tennis |
| Transport     | jet-ski | roller     | train | tram       |

 